{"tid":1846824,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位黑警 想救自己家人就請輕手對勇武","createTime":"2020-01-27T18:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T14:13:39.000Z","uid":123774,"like":65,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"78c43456e0527a6962857519489d57e94e2f5497","tid":1846824,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:00:10.000Z","msg":"我相信你地都知呢場疫症有幾嚴重<br />\n亦都想盡辦法想保護自己屋企人<br />\n你唔夠膽做嘅嘢 有人幫你做緊<br />\n請你諗清楚應該點樣對待勇武"},{"pid":"980cdcaa477f739d3be53a0edec2b4234350f6b9","tid":1846824,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:02:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">學校停 康文設施都停<br />\n啲人就湧晒去唔停嘅中心<br />\n社區爆發岌岌可危<br />\n<br />\n<ins>要求立即停止所有非緊急服務</ins></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99a20da3caceafafc8721498fc87e9c88dd2d0d0","tid":1846824,"uid":123774,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:06:02.000Z","msg":"你哋應該清楚知道香港人根本冇本錢去打呢場疫症<br />\n連正常生活行出街普通口罩都唔夠<br />\n病菌一入社區 響人口咁密集嘅地方就即刻全面爆發<br />\n依家仲要犧牲我哋醫護/資源去救班衝關大話精free rider<br />\n我希望你哋好好諗清楚呢次應該點選擇"},{"pid":"bdb08a41729f55afc689bb90df8aac568786dbb4","tid":1846824,"uid":123774,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:08:19.000Z","msg":"若然繼續咁多帶菌者衝關<br />\n作為執法部門你一定會被拖落水<br />\n為自己 為家人 為香港<br />\n請你三思應該點對待勇武"},{"pid":"658e5d93014e886e97a291cf9864ef99ce3affec","tid":1846824,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:10:24.000Z","msg":"[事關重大請廣傳]<br />\n<br />\n香港醫護、海關唔罷工嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護自己在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/edG0Z6X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FedG0Z6X.jpg&h=8ac5b79d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，一齊罷工保護香港，直至港府落實封關"},{"pid":"e586ce963092054f4b798d21b773d282250dbc6c","tid":1846824,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17e227c1822a361a30592180e128b1044b0ea12","tid":1846824,"uid":52520,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:25:29.000Z","msg":"佢老母有腦就唔使做黑警啦  <br />\n佢未死未病撚識驚咩  總之有得打 有女食 阿sir我就開心架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd49f718823a616524641140b03d98253e1235e","tid":1846824,"uid":38462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:27:09.000Z","msg":"想睇啊sir護送肺炎病人"},{"pid":"9bc4e9011887964626252450bb3f126d63ab6e1d","tid":1846824,"uid":10998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:23:45.000Z","msg":"傻啦,佢地係微博仲叫D支那人過黎香港睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f00497e6da720d2550cedfa037b074c15130c1","tid":1846824,"uid":66528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:34:32.000Z","msg":"都知班警甴狗改不了吃屎<br />\n<br />\n但你哋同你啲狗乸曱甴仔都係住喺香港<br />\n<br />\n俾班支那入到嚟你哋都死撚緊 <br />\n<br />\n你仲想同狗乸扑嘢嘅就咪撚阻止燒毒工作"},{"pid":"7b361b772ddcfe3db3e5d744fec05eb9572bba7b","tid":1846824,"uid":5523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:35:15.000Z","msg":"唔認同<br />\n天腳底我都要三萬隻狗死全家"},{"pid":"e6c4114